==English==

===Etymology===
{{L.}} ''[[recludere]]'' to unclose, open; prefix ''[[re-]]'' again, back, ''[[un-]] + [[claudere]]'' to shut.

===Verb===
'''reclude'''
# {{archaic}} To open again; to [[reopen]].
# once again include something that was excluded (a variation of "reinclude").
#:''Please '''reclude''' me in future discussions.''